  示例: "投保人手机号13800138000的客户" → {"field": "polNoInfo.applicantphoneno", "operator": "MATCH", "value": "13800138000"}

- **policies_beneficiary_mobile** | 操作符: MATCH | 值类型: extract | 定义: 保单受益人手机号，嵌套字段

